---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | BrewYourBeing">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-28 pb-20 bg-brew-cream min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif text-brew-brown mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-brew-brown">Effective Date:</strong> February 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use our booking form or contact us, we may collect personal information including your name, email address, phone number, age, gender, occupation, and details about your mental health concerns. This information is collected solely to provide you with our counselling services.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your personal information is used to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
          <li>Schedule and manage your therapy appointments</li>
          <li>Prepare for your sessions and provide personalized care</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your appointments and our services</li>
          <li>Maintain clinical records as required by professional standards</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">3. Data Protection & Confidentiality</h2>
        <p>We take the protection of your personal data seriously. All information shared with BrewYourBeing, whether through our website or during sessions, is treated as strictly confidential. We follow the ethical guidelines set forth by the Rehabilitation Council of India and applicable data protection laws.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">4. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise share your personal information with third parties. Information may only be disclosed when required by law, or with your explicit written consent.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Clinical records are retained in accordance with professional and legal requirements. You may request access to or deletion of your personal data by contacting us.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">6. Cookies & Website Analytics</h2>
        <p>Our website may use basic cookies to improve your browsing experience. These do not collect personally identifiable information. No third-party tracking or advertising cookies are used.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
          <li>Access your personal data held by us</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data (subject to legal requirements)</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for data processing at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy-related concerns, please contact us at <a href="mailto:brewyourbeing@gmail.com" class="text-brew-light hover:text-brew-brown underline">brewyourbeing@gmail.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+916263121929" class="text-brew-light hover:text-brew-brown underline">+91 6263-121929</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-brew-brown hover:text-brew-light transition-colors font-medium">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
